title: PROSE AND KAHNS
description: Named "one of the best one-liner writers of his generation" by StageTime Magazine, Zack Kahn is a Los Angeles-based comedian and a Telly Award winning TV writer who has garnered millions of hits worldwide on his many video sketches. He has been featured on Comedy Central Insider, L.A. Times' Metromix, VH1's Best Week Ever, Break.com and has written over 100 TV commercials and sketches.PROSE AND KAHNS is a collection of handpicked observations presented on the napkins, reciepts and scraps on which they were originally written.
author: Zack Kahn
